      "summary": "Bloomberg Intelligence's Athanasios Psarofagis joins Scarlet Fu and Katie Greifeld on \"Bloomberg ETF IQ.\". An ETF designed to track White House Policy has been in limbo for more than a year, as exchanges steer clear of what looks like a high-volatility, politically sensitive trade. The potential GRFT ETF is easily outperforming the S&amp;P 500 this year. (Source: Bloomberg)",
